      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car has been my baby\u2014it\u2019s in pristine condition and looks just like it did the day it left the showroom! Everything is spotless and it runs like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
