    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54 straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain sharp thanks to a pristine subframe and original bushings. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation, while the interior boasts unblemished Nappa leather. Meticulously maintained with a full documented service history, this is a collector-spec machine for the discerning purist.",
