      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean. Inside, the cabin is in a 'time capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing on the bolsters, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. All onboard technology, including the premium audio system and climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a full, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been driven sparingly and only in fair weather, ensuring the engine bay and mechanical components are in showroom condition. This listing represents a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a flagship vehicle in its most pristine form. Complete service records, original keys, and a clean title are included. Professional inspections are welcomed and encouraged.",
